<div data-morris-national-target="phase" data-phase="hero" style="min-height: 100dvh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 80px 28px 56px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
  <%# Background orbs %>
  <div style="position: absolute; top: 5%; left: -6%; width: 360px; height: 360px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--mn-accent-l); filter: blur(90px); opacity: 0.5; pointer-events: none;"></div>
  <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 7%; right: -5%; width: 280px; height: 280px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--mn-accent-l); filter: blur(75px); opacity: 0.38; pointer-events: none;"></div>

  <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 580px;">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <span style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mn-muted);">
        Morris National &middot; Founded 1950
      </span>
      <span style="font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mn-accent); background: var(--mn-accent-l); border: 1.5px solid var(--mn-border); border-radius: 100px; padding: 3px 10px;">
        Annual Growth Scenario
      </span>
    </div>

    <h1 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(36px, 8.5vw, 62px); font-weight: 500; color: var(--mn-text); line-height: 1.08; margin: 0 0 18px;">
      How Saulto would protect Morris National's annual goal
    </h1>

    <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 4vw, 20px); color: var(--mn-muted); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0 0 10px;">
      A scenario showing how Saulto tracks the probability of hitting Morris National's annual goal, catches what threatens it, and tells you exactly what to do before it becomes a problem you are explaining.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--mn-border); margin: 0 0 44px;">
      Confectionery, gifting, seasonal. US and Canada. All connected.
    </p>

    <button data-action="click->morris-national#advance"
      style="background: var(--mn-accent); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 100px; cursor: pointer; padding: 17px 44px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.04em;">
      Watch it play out
    </button>

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--mn-border); margin-top: 26px;">
      7 screens. Takes about 3 minutes.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 10px; color: var(--mn-border); margin-top: 14px; max-width: 340px; line-height: 1.5; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
      This is an illustrative scenario built on publicly available information about Morris National and standard business practices. All figures are illustrative.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
